data.description: WELCOME HOME! This property is located in the sought-after Archer school district. You will enjoy the private fenced back yard perfect for playing or entertaiment. The Kitchen opens up into the Family Room with a cozy fireplace, creating a perfect setting for relaxation. Formal living room with plenty of natural light plus dinning room that opens up to the living room area. Walk-in closet and renovated bathroom in master bedroom.Three additional bedrooms are located upstairs providing ample space for work and play. Easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss this opportunity to own a stunning home in one of Grayson's most desirable neighborhoods.
